Sasha Mitchell https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sasha_Mitchell 0 Sasha Mitchell (born July 27, 1967) is an American actor best known for his television roles as James Beaumont on Dallas and Cody Lambert on Step by Step. Mitchell also holds a black belt in Tae Kwon Do.
